title: Gorgeous renovated 2BR in S Mpls $1450
posting_body: ['Monthly rent payment: $1,450', '^', 'KEY FEATURES:', 'Sq.', 'footage: 1,000', 'Bedrooms; 2', 'Bathroom: 1', 'Lease duration: 12 months', 'Deposit: $1,450', 'Non-smoking building; no drugs', 'Pet policy: sorry, no dogs, cat deposit of $150', 'Laundry: provided in basement (not coin-operated)', 'Floor/level: Second floor of two-story building', 'Property type: Fourplex', 'Occupancy: limited to two people per bedroom', 'HIGHLIGHTS:', 'Fully renovated 2-bedroom apartment with tall ceilings in South Minneapolis.', 'Stunning brand new kitchen with stainless steel appliances.', 'Beautiful dark wood trim, including a built-in buffet in the dining room.', 'Refinished wood floors throughout.', 'Brand new bathroom with gorgeous subway tile.', 'Well maintained building with a responsive property manager.', 'Quick walk to the Midtown Global Market, and access to the Midtown Greenway bike/walk path is just a block away.', 'Easy access to I-35W and mass transit, and close proximity to all that downtown Minneapolis, Uptown, Eat Street, the Seward neighborhood, and the University of Minnesota have to offer.', 'RENTAL FEATURES:', 'Gas range/oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Water, sewer, and garbage included in rent.', 'Tenant pays gas and electric.', 'PARKING:', 'On-street parking available.', 'One single-stall, detached garage is available for an additional $50/month.', 'LEASE TERMS:', "All prospective tenants are required to fill out an application verifying income (rent can be no more than 1/3 of renter's income), rental history, and a credit score of at least 675.", 'A criminal background check will be conducted.', 'Tenant responsible for $40 application fee.']
